name: Software Engineer
description: Able to take on larger and more impactful engineering responsibility, with less guidance. Is communicating on a wider level.

name: Associate Engineer
description: Just starting their engineering career. Learning how to take on and complete small tasks, work with immediate peers, and communicate appropriately.

name: Senior Software Engineer
description:
Leading major engineering initiatives, with little to no guidance. 

Is communicating on a team-wide level.

name: Engineering Manager
description: Leading a small team of engineers. Involved in hiring. Communicates on a team level.

name: Senior UX Designer
description: Leading major product design projects, with little to no guidance. Is communicating on a team-wide level, and responsible for a significant set of areas.
